  "title": "Lead Generation / Inside Sales Executive",
  "description": "<h3>🔹 <strong>Job Title: Lead Generation / Inside Sales Executive</strong></h3>\n<p>📍 Location: [Marymount] | 🕒 Full-Time | 💼 Basic + <strong>Incentives</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Are you a go-getter with a passion for connecting with people and uncovering business opportunities? We’re looking for a motivated <strong>Lead Generation / Inside Sales Executive</strong> to help us grow our client base and support our sales team.</p>\n<h3><strong>What You’ll Be Doing:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proactively reach out to potential clients via phone, email, and online channels</li>\n  <li>Research and identify key decision-makers across target industries</li>\n  <li>Qualify leads and pass them to the sales team for follow-up</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate records of all activities in the CRM system</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with the sales team to schedule meetings and demos</li>\n  <li>Keep up to date with product knowledge to speak confidently with prospects</li>\n  <li>Achieve weekly/monthly KPIs for outreach and conversions</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What You Bring:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min. Diploma in Business, Marketing, or related field</li>\n  <li>1+ year of experience in lead generation, inside sales, or telemarketing preferred</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated, energetic, and results-driven</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with CRM tools is a bonus</li>\n</ul>\n<p>🚀 If you're eager to grow your career in sales and thrive in a fast-paced, goal-oriented environment—we’d love to hear from you!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>WeCruit Pte Ltd</strong> | EA License No. <strong>20C0270</strong><br>\nEA Personnel: <strong>Tan Soon Hock (Steven)</strong> | Registration No. <strong>R1109889</strong></p>",
